## Description of Service

KibblRx is a pet medication tracking application that allows you to manage medication schedules, log symptoms, generate reports, and receive reminders. The app stores data locally on your device and optionally syncs via your personal iCloud account.

## Subscriptions and Payments

KibblRx offers a free tier and an optional premium subscription, KibblRx+.

- **Monthly Subscription:** $2.99/month, billed monthly
- **Yearly Subscription:** $19.99/year, billed annually
- **Lifetime Purchase:** $49.99, one-time non-recurring payment

Subscriptions are processed through your Apple ID account. Payment is charged at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the same price.

You can manage and cancel subscriptions by going to your device Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions.

Free trial periods, if offered, will automatically convert to a paid subscription at the end of the trial unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the trial ends. Any unused portion of a free trial is forfeited upon purchasing a subscription.

